title: Starting with the Transmigration
description: Starting with the Transmigration In a world where the path to immortality is broken, Lu Cheng, a cursed travellers, becomes the only person who can attract the heavenly tribulation. At the moment of death, the mysterious system is activated, Lu Cheng is determined to become stronger and change his fate, and upgrade himself by crossing the tribulation! Sun, Moon, and Death …… is the end of the world? The most important thing is that the system is not only a way of life, but also a way of life. The heavenly dao slaughter mortal dust, floating life cause and effect between the fingers. A sword blade open chaos, three lives of fate and calamity to laugh! The road to immortality, starting from the sabotage! Beginning From Passing Through the Calamity Cong Du Jie Kai Shi Crossing the Calamity Cóng Dù Jié Kāi Shǐ It All Starts With Breakthrough Starting From Calamity Crossing Starting With the Transmigration 从渡劫开始 Breaking through the Calamity
alternative_titles: Beginning From Passing Through the Calamity
